HEADWORD: Deoxidizer
<hw>De*ox"i*di`zer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>That which removes oxygen; hence, a reducing agent; <as>as, nascent
hydrogen is a <ex>deoxidizer</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Deoxygenate</ent>⟦br⟧
